text.tspan: Proportion of local livestock breeds at risk of extinction, 2024
Share of local livestock breeds which are classified as being at risk of extinction. Breed-related information
remains far from complete. For almost 60 percent of all reported breeds, risk status is not known because of
missing population data or lack of recent updates.
Data source: Food and Agriculture Organization of the United Nations
